title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: Exception is thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in a group row.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in a group row.
SR: To reproduce the bug: 1. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 2. Preview the attached report. 3. Attempt to export the data from the table and observe if an exception is thrown.
